撚狗咁撚螢火同朱絹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n套野根本唔係講咩打鬥同暗殺 <br />\n由頭到尾都係講佢地兩個相愛 但不能相戀 既愛情片<br />\n第一集 阿伯一針刺阿婆果到先最有張力"},{"pid":"3cc412b8abf077c55ebdf4899fa87cf3876a16cf","tid":434201,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"一定要有胡夷咁既女角色先好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bea7048bb23a09df1154b7b5be7fa3475ec531","tid":434201,"uid":101219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"陰陽座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8780ea7c95fbf1d28b8b1dd903ea1063b1539e","tid":434201,"uid":52124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"兩個老野一齊死果part好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5430835c7cdb7c22e1dbebc10f8d1f39343fa4cd","tid":434201,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔計主角同puma呢兩個外掛<br />\n其實甲賀d人既忍術係比較偏向暗殺同功能<br />\n係得個肥仔同蜘蛛佬 叫戰鬥系<br />\n如果講好打 隻抽應該就伊賀既好打d</blockquote><br />\n唔計眼其實對甲賀唔公平<br />\n因為甲賀有兩條友都係靠眼<br />\n計埋既話就甲賀羸 因為朧冇得同時望兩條友<br />\n<br />\n如果要唔計咁起馬甲賀要多條唔係用眼既人<br />\n或者唔計伊賀既不死淫賊 反正佢都只係個不死超級小兵"},{"pid":"2711e6df6d48c4b5f8f43b755f185515380f6b88","tid":434201,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"小學睇過記得有一集係個女主比人女女女<br />\n個男伸手入條女個波列到果下衝擊差d流鼻血<br />\n之後晚晚追都好似冇甜弓弓"},{"pid":"df9bd640d65e8132437c8929da6e243117a2b5c2","tid":434201,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學睇過記得有一集係個女主比人女女女<br />\n個男伸手入條女個波列到果下衝擊差d流鼻血<br />\n之後晚晚追都好似冇甜<span style=\"color: red;\">了</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"026b8637067fa76069a4bfdbdd176