":434201,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"其實成套野最好睇唔係佢地既忍術有幾勁或戰鬥幾精彩<br />\n而係作者將20人既戰鬥描寫到好似戰爭咁，鬥情報、手段<br />\n你忍術幾勁都無用，一俾人知道左就死緊，男女主角除外"},{"pid":"191b9cbcafbe1de02431c3acb29e28489361a01b","tid":434201,"uid":52876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:57:05.000Z","msg":"好似唔係山田風太郎作, 咁都算續作?"},{"pid":"bcf9b11fd48628164655bff6f971e48f5b9553fd","tid":434201,"uid":56430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"弦之介一開眼就見到朧死係面前<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd240fd97d551606a4e33ded967ae218f16ee1f","tid":434201,"uid":49293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"頭先睇漫畫睇到最新  續集d忍術咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4fb70e860ec98f4d1315228acb0c05c7797204","tid":434201,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套野值得一睇<br />\n<br />\n但D死法好ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好打最型果個夜叉丸 咩人都冇殺過就咁死左<br />\n本身睇完第一集以為D打鬥應該會好好睇 呃哂<br />\n但次次都係隱型大隻佬成個HITMAN咁一下偷偷地殺死<br />\n一係就果個易容佬又係一刀斬死人<br />\n個易容佬一次都話丫 幾次啊<br />\n明明已經知道左佢個能力都仲要咁ON9一D防備都冇<br />\n<br />\n最好睇都係第一集</blockquote><br />\n咁先似忍者喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c17f316429f9834447d06884421030200f4109e","tid":434201,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"時間上2代隔左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7a5b9d6df017f1590da3ed66a2f77c86bfd9e6","tid":434201,"uid":13808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間上2代隔左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10年，好似"},{"pid":"5a53ecba2dbd9e37115d14cad035e4c9ccb2e38b","tid":434201,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實成套野最好睇唔係佢地既忍術有幾勁或戰鬥幾精彩<br />\n而係作者將20人既戰鬥描寫到好似戰爭咁，鬥情報、手段<br />\n你忍術幾勁都無用，一俾人知道左就死緊，男女主角除外</blockquote><br />\n左衛門 易容能力一早比人知道左喇WO 咁點解冇事既?<br />\n仲輕輕鬆鬆殺左兩條友<br />\n一開始比人破左易容果時仲係間咁細既木屋到輕鬆一野跳走<br />\n明明身邊有幾個高手忍者圍住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fc0aa6a69bb360089aa6198a785b204a6e9946","tid":434201,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇擠波真係唔會睇嚕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫版露波但冇lin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會無，朱絹咪露左</blockquote><br />\n痴女朱絹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedeeecb19e033db2545086e8a8779660095ce0c","tid":434201,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"上網睇左漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都幾鳩下<br />\n<br />\n開始劇透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">屌你老味 400年既世仇邊可能10年後就樂也融融<br />\n10年前話開得拖個個都幾開心,依家大家會得閒切磋下個轉變我覺得太大了<br />\n仲要舊人D同族1個都入唔到十忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出1,2個懷舊下都好啦<br />\n能力平衡果到仲慘原本係反傷同破能力 合左變神威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (可能團戰有用 但效果一定冇反傷咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n仲有個孔雀 頭5話死1,2個敵役當閒角咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家作到佢真係不死身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"44e9f4446fa13f8fe980f6c8c46b80233ca8620f","tid":434201,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"唔知各位巴打有無睇原著小說<br />\n好 撚 好 睇 ！<br />\n我買唔齊佢啲小說但可以買既都盡買<br />\n甲賀本小說我睇左不下十次<br />\n其他都好撚正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但想問知唔知櫻花忍法帖個故事邊個寫？<br />\n因為山田先生死左喇喎"},{"pid":"de92be0d9ee35a34a92c21c070da999956319a9c","tid":434201,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"胡夷死果刻，左衛門捉住佢隻手指，好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02b9ada1992774431a7a2edebe57f4ad531246c","tid":434201,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個每一晚星期六都追<br />\n七武士、甲賀忍法帖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年嗰個時段嘅動畫極高質<br />\n仲有鴉、Monster、火鳥、高橋留美子劇場、人魚之森</blockquote><br />\n全部讀緊小五打後既入哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捉鬼天狗幫呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b2acff9556c939c6d3c078bc328bf9da4a8b4f","tid":434201,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最記得天膳好撚淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係架船上面女女女朧<br />\n同埋同果個毒吻女打車輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朧真係好撚好J，細個睇比佢女女女個幕扯到行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}